freqtab <- function( # 
        x, # 
        cn=1+log2(length(x)), # 
        wid=FALSE ) # 
{
    x <- x[!is.na(x)] # 
    min <- min(x) # 
    max <- max(x) # 
    ran <- max - min # 
    if(!wid){ wid <- round(abs(ran/cn), 3) } # 
    cla <- floor(x/wid) # 
    mnc <- min(cla) # 
    mxc <- max(cla) # 
    cla <- factor(cla, levels=mnc:mxc) # 
    freq <- table(cla) # 
    names(freq) <- paste(mnc:mxc*wid, "-", mnc:mxc*wid+wid) # 
    percent <- round(freq/sum(freq)*100,2) # %
    cum.pcnt <- round(cumsum(percent),2) # %
    return(cbind(freq, percent, cum.pcnt)) # 
}
